# Keeps the gallery/ directory present in git and the Docker/Cloud Build context.
# Real NAIP scene thumbnails now live here: s01.png … s15.png (720×720, see gallery-data.js).
# There is no separate IR set — each scene's `rgb` and `ir` both point at sNN.png.
# The ESRI-tile fallback (wireSceneFallback) only triggers if one of these is missing.